Hii! 👋🏽👋🏽
1. @kaylabrenda n I having fun with pano mode at the park. 

2. A fun project I decided to start & finish (WIP 🚧) with my own vocals on the track. Trying to break my crippling fear of people hearing my voice/musicianship!

3. Also me getting over my crippling fear of breaking my neck!!! BUT WE GOT THE BACK HAND SPRING BACK! 

4. I met a girl on the river in Colorado! 
 
5. Picked her up and gave her a ride on my paddle board! 

6. A MF LEGEND! My mom is so special to me and I truly cherish all the time we get to spend together. ILY🖤

Appreciate all the positive feedback and continuous plays on my Muddy Feet remix! Im really excited to push this project forward as much as possible and to keep putting out quality tracks! Also LINK IN BIO for the song! 👾 🙌🏽
